::Aerotaur::
       "Nothing to worry about.  I'm sure I have weapons somewhere."  He 
searches his body.  "Ah there we go."  Two pieces of his arm snap into place 
forming a bow.  He pulls back a lever on his arm and an energy arrow forms.  
Aiming at a tree he fires the arrow.  It pierces three trees before fading.  
"I think we can handle it."

--part1_191.971ec42.2a5b04ca_boundary
